svg.title: Comparison of several satellite navigation system orbits
svg.desc: Comparison of GPS, GLONASS, Galileo and COMPASS (medium earth orbit satellites) orbits with International Space Station, Hubble Space Telescope, Iridium Constellation and geostationary orbits, and the nominal size of the earth, drawn by CMG Lee. Earth bitmap is http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:North_pole_february_ice-pack_1978-2002.png by Geo Swan.
